<p>I have a template that receives a <code>string</code> as its data type:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;DataTemplate x:DataType="System:String"&gt;    &lt;TextBlock Text="{x:Bind}" /&gt; &lt;/DataTemplate&gt; </code></pre>  <p>But this binding technique gives me a build error. How can I use <code>{x:Bind}</code> without a path value? I want to bind <strong>the string</strong>, not a property in the string.</p>